&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;Why Visit Split?
 &lt;div id="why-visit-split" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#why-visit-split" aria-label="Anchor"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ferry.techpawz.com/posts/hvar-to-split-ferry/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;Split&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://cruise.techpawz.com/posts/dubrovnik_shore-excursions/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;Croatia&lt;/a&gt;, is a vibrant coastal city that beautifully marries history with modernity. Nestled along the stunning Adriatic Sea, it boasts a rich history that dates back to the Roman Empire. The city is home to the magnificent Diocletian&amp;rsquo;s Palace, a UNESCO World Heritage site that forms the heart of Split and offers a glimpse into its storied past. As you wander through its ancient streets, you’ll encounter a mix of Roman ruins, medieval architecture, and a lively atmosphere that perfectly captures the essence of Mediterranean life.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>